      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little cosmetic work. The exterior has some noticeable scuffs on the bumpers and a bit of clear coat peeling on the roof, while the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car at a fair price for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag.",
