    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is ready for a total transformation and could be the perfect foundation for your next big build. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a classic model at an entry-level price. If you\u2019re looking for a rewarding challenge and a car with potential, this is the one for you!",
