    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the paint is heavily oxidized. Mechanically, it requires major repairs to the engine and transmission to be safely drivable, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It is sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
